a right parking lock mechanism (6) which locks a rotation of the right wheel (3RR), the right parking lock mechanism (6) comprising a locking operation prevention mechanism (63c,63d) which mechanically prevents a locking operation of the right parking lock mechanism (6) when a wheel rotation speed of the right wheel (3RR) exceeds a predetermined parking lock prevention wheel rotation speed;

